p: The volatile compounds were tentatively identified by comparing their mass spectra with those in the NIST27 and NIST147 libraries (considering a minimum similarity of 85%) and by retention indices obtained from www.pherobase.com [ 27] or www.flavornet.org [ 28] (for columns with a similar stationary phase to ZB-5 ms). The results were expressed as a percentage of the total peaks area.
